<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Cisco SDCI + SD-WAN Neocloud Framework</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --cisco-blue: #049fd9;
      --cisco-dark: #0d274d;
      --cisco-light: #f4f8fb;
      --text: #1f2937;
      --muted: #6b7280;
      --card: #ffffff;
      --border: #dbe4ee;
      --success: #0f9d58;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body {
      font-family: "Segoe UI", Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      color: var(--text);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f7fbff 0%, #eef6fc 100%);
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 24px;
    }

    header {
      background: linear-gradient(120deg, var(--cisco-dark), var(--cisco-blue));
      color: #fff;
      padding: 56px 24px;
      border-bottom: 6px solid #7fd3f7;
    }

    .hero-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .hero-subtitle {
      max-width: 860px;
      color: #d9f2ff;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
    }

    .pill-row {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: 18px;
    }

    .pill {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.35);
      padding: 6px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
    }

    main {
      padding: 28px 0 48px;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      color: var(--cisco-dark);
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .section-intro {
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      max-width: 900px;
    }

    .grid-3 {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .card {
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 22px rgba(13, 39, 77, 0.06);
    }

    .card h3 {
      color: var(--cisco-blue);
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      font-size: 1.03rem;
    }

    .card p {
      color: #374151;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .diagram {
      margin-top: 16px;
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 22px rgba(13, 39, 77, 0.06);
    }

    .diagram h3 {
      color: var(--cisco-dark);
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .flow {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr auto 1fr;
      gap: 10px;
      align-items: center;
      margin: 8px 0 14px;
    }

    .node {
      border: 1px solid #b9d9ea;
      background: #f5fbff;
      color: #0f2f57;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 14px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 0.93rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      min-height: 72px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .arrow {
      color: var(--cisco-blue);
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .bullet-list {
      margin-top: 8px;
      padding-left: 18px;
      color: #374151;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .bullet-list li {
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .marketplace-strip {
      margin-top: 18px;
      border: 1px dashed #9ecde3;
      background: #f2fbff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 14px;
    }

    .marketplace-strip strong {
      color: var(--cisco-dark);
    }

    .kpi-row {
      margin-top: 20px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .kpi {
      background: white;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 14px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .kpi .value {
      color: var(--success);
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .kpi .label {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      margin-top: 3px;
    }

    footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      color: #6b7280;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 12px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .grid-3 {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .flow {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .arrow {
        transform: rotate(90deg);
        text-align: center;
      }

      .kpi-row {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 520px) {
      .hero-title {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
      }

      .kpi-row {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-title">Enterprise Framework: SDCI Procurement + Cisco SD-WAN for Neocloud</div>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">
        A reference model for enterprises to procure SD-WAN via Solutions+/GPL, extend secure connectivity through SDCI,
        and consume AI Inference-as-a-Service marketplaces (e.g., OpenRouter) with policy-driven traffic engineering.
      </p>
      <div class="pill-row">
        <span class="pill">Solutions+ / GPL</span>
        <span class="pill">Cisco SD-WAN</span>
        <span class="pill">SDCI Interconnect</span>
        <span class="pill">Neocloud Access</span>
        <span class="pill">Inference Marketplaces</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="container">
    <section>
      <h2 class="section-title">Framework Layers</h2>
      <p class="section-intro">
        This model aligns commercial procurement, network onboarding, and AI-service consumption in one operational pattern.
      </p>

      <div class="grid-3">
        <article class="card">
          <h3>1) Procurement Layer</h3>
          <p>
            Acquire Cisco SD-WAN components through Solutions+ and GPL motions. Bundle virtual network functions and SDCI
            connectivity options into enterprise procurement workflows.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
          <h3>2) Connectivity Layer</h3>
          <p>
            Use Cisco SD-WAN with SDCI for secure, deterministic paths into Neocloud environments. Apply segmentation,
            app-aware routing, and centralized policy through vManage.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
          <h3>3) Consumption Layer</h3>
          <p>
            Publish/enable Cisco SD-WAN connectivity in provider marketplaces and product catalogs, supporting
            Inference-as-a-Service providers and exchanges such as OpenRouter.
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="diagram">
      <h3>Reference Architecture Flow</h3>

      <div class="flow">
        <div class="node">Enterprise Branch / DC<br>(Users, Apps, Data)</div>
        <div class="arrow">➜</div>
        <div class="node">Cisco SD-WAN Fabric<br>(Policy + Segmentation)</div>
        <div class="arrow">➜</div>
        <div class="node">SDCI / Neocloud Edge<br>(Private Interconnect)</div>
      </div>

      <div class="flow">
        <div class="node">Neocloud GPU Zones<br>(Model Hosting)</div>
        <div class="arrow">➜</div>
        <div class="node">Inference Marketplace<br>(OpenRouter-style Catalog)</div>
        <div class="arrow">➜</div>
        <div class="node">Enterprise AI Apps<br>(Low-latency Inference)</div>
      </div>

      <ul class="bullet-list">
        <li>Enable catalog-based service ordering for SD-WAN + SDCI bundles.</li>
        <li>Attach marketplace destinations as policy objects in SD-WAN templates.</li>
        <li>Steer inference traffic by SLA: latency, jitter, loss, and cost profile.</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="marketplace-strip">
        <strong>Marketplace Enablement:</strong>
        Expose “Cisco SD-WAN Connectivity for AI Inference” as a productized offer in provider marketplaces/catalogs,
        allowing enterprises to subscribe and activate transport + policy in a guided onboarding flow.
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="section-title" style="margin-top:20px;">Target Outcomes</h2>
      <div class="kpi-row">
        <div class="kpi">
          <div class="value">Faster</div>
          <div class="label">Procurement to Activation</div>
        </div>
        <div class="kpi">
          <div class="value">Lower</div>
          <div class="label">Inference Path Latency</div>
        </div>
        <div class="kpi">
          <div class="value">Higher</div>
          <div class="label">Policy & Security Control</div>
        </div>
        <div class="kpi">
          <div class="value">Scalable</div>
          <div class="label">Multi-Provider AI Access</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer>
    © 2026 Cisco-inspired reference layout for SDCI + SD-WAN + Neocloud + Inference Marketplace integration
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
